			<section>
									<div class="summary">
						<p>A <code>Collection</code> of tests that represents a test group.</p>
					</div>
				
									<div class="description">
						<p>Tests are added to this group either on <code>construct</code> by passing a fully-namespaced test class
or namespace string-based path, e.g.</p>
<pre><code class="language-php">$group = new Group(['data' =&gt; [
    'data\ModelTest',
    new \lithium\tests\cases\core\ObjectTest()
]]);
</code></pre>
<p>Or they can be added programmatically:</p>
<pre><code class="language-php">$group-&gt;add('data\ModelTest');
</code></pre>
					</div>
